    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors are not assessed, consistent with MRL 2 requirements. The model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Note: the Model inputs factor rationale acknowledges that re-validation against the post-revision experimental dataset is planned; the assessment team considers the existing evidence sufficient for the current submission cycle pending completion of that activity.",
